{
  "texts": [
    "The optimal approximation can be found by constructing the LagrangianL = i 2 ⟨ψ(z)|ψ(z)⟩ -1 m,i [ żim ⟨ψ(z)|∂ im ψ(z)⟩ -żim ⟨∂ im ψ(z)|ψ(z)⟩] - ⟨ψ(z)|H|ψ(z)⟩ ⟨ψ(z)|ψ(z)⟩,(72)where ∂ im = ∂ ∂zim (and similarly for ∂im).",
